tartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"히나","body":"어~디? 「파스파레 엄청난 스캔들!\n립싱크&거짓 퍼포먼스가 데뷔 당일 들통나」……?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"band4-006-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"기사 댓글","body":"「보컬 아야는 아이돌 경험자잖아?」\n「경험자라고 해봤자 고작 연습생. 그럴만한 성과는 없었지.」","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"기사 댓글","body":"「간신히 데뷔했는데.\n아야 짱, 어떻게 되는 걸까……」","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"기사 댓글","body":"「베이스는 원래 아역이었던 시라사기 치사토였지?\n연주도 하는 척이라니 역시 연기파 아역이구나ㅋ」\n「연기파라는 명성은 거짓이 아니었네」","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"아야","body":"……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"band4-006-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requi